<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>nạṣf ṣbḥy</author>
<title>klạmk ạ̉yạ rb nwry</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kalạmuka ạảyā rabũ nūrī
 hūa hudāya fī ạl̊masīr̊
 (bihi ʿaraf̊tu kaẙfa ạảtaẙta
 kaẙfa fadaẙta yā qadīr̊)2

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: (sirājuⁿ lirij̊lī kalạmuka
 wanūruⁿ lisabīlī)2

[V3]
 2- hūa ḍīāyỉy was̊ṭa ạlẓãlạmi
 hūa ạảnīsu riḥ̊latī
 (fīhi gẖidẖāyỉy fīhi salạmī
 ʿazāyỉy waq̊ta miḥ̊natī)2

[V4]
 3- sāʿid̊nī ḥatãy̱ ạủkẖabĩyảnã
 kalạmaka dākẖil̊ qal̊bī
 (falạ ạảʿūda ạủkẖ̊ṭī ại̹laẙka
 bal̊ yasẖ̊hadu laka ḥubĩy)</lyrics>
</song>